            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in 1.0.3</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Context-aware actions</strong>: show only relevant items based on selection + file types</li>
                    <li><strong>Import/Export window</strong>: reliable script import/export flow</li>
                    <li><strong>Background execution</strong>: running actions no longer steals focus</li>
                    <li><strong>Polish</strong>: optional notifications, menu bar icon + Dock visibility toggles, update menu</li>
                </ul>
                ]]>
